        <title>Basic script to insert a simple timestamp</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[sylumer]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>You could also just use the following text in an Insert Text action to go the opposite direction and do it in one line no scripting (thanks to Drafts’ template engine). <img src="https://forums.getdrafts.com/images/emoji/apple/wink.png?v=9" title=":wink:" class="emoji" alt=":wink:"></p>
<pre><code class="lang-auto">[[date|%H:%M]] 
</code></pre>
