      <item>
        <title>Basic script to insert a simple timestamp</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[scripts4drafts]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Hi,</p>
<p>indeed, the Insert Text action is easier.</p>
<p>Just for fun, here is the script with your request:</p>
<pre><code>let loc = editor.getSelectedRange()[0],
  now = new Date().toTimeString().slice(0, 5);
editor.setTextInRange(loc, 0, now + ' ');
editor.setSelectedRange(loc + 6, 0);</code></pre>
          <p><a href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/t/basic-script-to-insert-a-simple-timestamp/3994/5">Read full topic</a></p>
